; Coverage test for post.cc line 364:
; Exercise any(EXPR, false) to exclude self from the test.
; When false is passed as second arg, the current posting is excluded.

2024/01/01 Mixed
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash     $-10.00

test reg --limit "any(account =~ /Food/, false)" Assets
24-Jan-01 Mixed                 Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
end test
